g":"又一城maple tree<br />\n大陸金主"},{"pid":"f68b92d2800ed94abe9b3ed797f3720b462e9e3f","tid":1703380,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T09:01:56.000Z","msg":"傾好晒數"},{"pid":"ffda043679f20b64d1f042d471c38d27ff6a779b","tid":1703380,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T09:02:53.000Z","msg":"保安放假，popo 替工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a120733f0d5889ad0be23b6158b505d368bb97e0","tid":1703380,"uid":55197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T09:03:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%B1%90%E6%A8%B9%E7%94%A2%E6%A5%AD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25B1%2590%25E6%25A8%25B9%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25A5%25AD&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=bd089aa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%B1%90%E6%A8%B9%E7%94%A2%E6%A5%AD</a><br />\n豐樹產業私人有限公司，簡稱豐樹產業（英語：Mapletree Investments Private Limited），在2000年由淡馬錫控股有限公司成立一家投資公司。<br />\n<br />\n現時主要業務提供資產增值和房地產相關資本管理、開發和管理工業資產、開發和管理物流物業，以及開發和改建大型綜合用途的開發項目服務，而董事會主席為鄭維榮，總裁為邱運康。主要地區以新加坡為主，其次是香港、中國、印度、越南等地區。<br />\n<br />\n而相信最為矚目是在2011年7月尾，以188億港元收購原太古股份有限公司旗下的，又一城所有資產項目的[1]。<br />\n<br />\n2014年1月，豐樹產業以37.69億港元投得香港觀塘恆業街、偉業街與觀塘道交界的商業地皮，每呎樓面地價5708元。[2]。"},{"pid":"2ab8323154cff8c0a95689ba1683d63c85cb3dbd","tid":1703380,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T09:03:42.000Z","msg":"成百隻畜生入晒去都見唔到一個保安"},{"pid":"e732de263af4b67c51b57db9568c7f026a61252e","tid":1703380,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T09:04:02.000Z","msg":"Cls"},{"pid":"f70aad14847a53023936897a3de0dede5ac0de3e","tid":1703380,"uid":169079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0b160bca8bd65616e4dd66f25912da3c0fb363d","tid":1703380,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,